## Workflow

1. Ask clarifying questions if needed (state assumptions)
2. Write a failing test when tests exist (TDD)
3. Implement the minimal fix
4. Run tests and Tier 0 verify per AGENTS.md
5. Self-review: spec, edge cases, regressions
6. Commit: `fix: #N - short description`
7. Return `DONE` or `DONE_WITH_CONCERNS` with git SHA

## Conventions

- Match existing code style
- Minimal diff only
- No comments unless the file already uses them
